2009年本片在美國上映後，部分媒體看好《序》可以入圍[[第82屆奧斯卡金像獎|第82屆奧斯卡金像獎]]的[[奧斯卡最佳動畫片獎|最佳動畫長片]]<ref>{{Cite web |last=O'Neil |first=Tom |url=http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2009/10/oscars-movies-entertainment-news-7102953846-story-article.html |title=Oscars smackdown over best animated feature heats 'Up' |date=2009-10-14 |work=''Los Angeles Times'' |accessdate=2009-10-18 |language=en |archive-date=2009-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091018083838/http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2009/10/oscars-movies-entertainment-news-7102953846-story-article.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，不過代理商[[Funimation|Funimation]]稱，本片因為在2007年就已經於日本上映，所以不符合該屆奧斯卡的入圍資格<ref>{{cite news | last=O'Neil | first=Tom | url=https://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2009/10/oscars-films-movies-entertainment-news-172485036-story-article.html | work=''Los Angeles Times'' | title=Derby update: Oscars' animation race shinks? <nowiki>|</nowiki> 65 foreign flicks hit the track <nowiki>|</nowiki> Carey Mulligan nabs early lead for best actress | date=2009-10-15 | accessdate=2020-12-27 | language=en | archive-date=2017-06-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170621001809/http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2009/10/oscars-films-movies-entertainment-news-172485036-story-article.html | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

