為了提升DVD的觀影體驗，總監督庵野微調了影像和-{音}-頻，共有266處<ref name="DVD Release"/>，不過故事和設定並沒有受到影響。DVD的特裝版限量30萬張<ref name="auctioning">{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-04-28/evangelion-film-strips-auctioning-for-up-to-y30000 |title=Evangelion Film Strips Auctioning for Up to Y152,000 (Updated) |date=2008-04-28 |work=Anime News Network |accessdate=2021-01-20 |language=en |archive-date=2017-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170627223848/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-04-28/evangelion-film-strips-auctioning-for-up-to-y30000 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，額外收錄一張光碟<ref name="每日-DVD"/>，當中收錄有標題為「Explanation of EVANGELION:1.01」的反射式字幕解說、屋島作戰BGM《Angel of Doom》的PV等特別收錄。比較特別的是，特裝版附贈有從院線放映用膠捲剪下來的隨機五幀影像<ref name="auctioning"/>，重要片段的膠捲在網路拍賣中高價售出，獲得媒體報導<ref name="每日-DVD">{{cite news |url=http://mainichi.jp/enta/mantan/news/20080428mog00m200010000c.html |script-title=ja:ヱヴァンゲリヲン：「おまけ」生フィルムに1万円超　オークションでプレミア化 |date=2008-04-28 |work=毎日jp |accessdate=2021-02-04 |language=ja |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080501141447/http://mainichi.jp/enta/mantan/news/20080428mog00m200010000c.html |archivedate=2008-05-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=「ヱヴァンゲリヲン新劇場版:序」のDVD特典フィルムに3万円以上のプレミア|url=https://gigazine.net/news/20080428_eva_film/|accessdate=2021-02-04|author=|date=2008-04-28|format=|work=GIGAZINE|publisher=|language=ja|archive-date=2020-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200502042136/https://gigazine.net/news/20080428_eva_film/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://mainichi.jp/enta/mantan/news/20080502mog00m200034000c.html |script-title=ja:特典「生フィルム」がプレミア化　綾波レイは20万円突破 |date=2008-05-02 |work=毎日jp |accessdate=2021-02-04 |language=ja |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080528133057/http://mainichi.jp/enta/mantan/news/20080502mog00m200034000c.html |archivedate=2008-05-28 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。根據[[Oricon|Oricon]]統計，本片的特裝版DVD在發行首週售出了21.9萬張，排名當週第一，同時也是《EVA》系列中家用媒體最暢銷的一部<ref>{{Cite web|title=新世代エヴァが過去最高の売上を記録！|url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/news/54169/full/|accessdate=2021-02-04|author=|date=2008-04-29|format=|work=ORICON NEWS|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2021-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210102233737/https://www.oricon.co.jp/news/54169/full/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mainichi.jp/enta/mantan/anime/news/20080428mog00m200052000c.html |script-title=ja:ヱヴァンゲリヲン：DVD22万枚で今年トップ　オリコンランキング |date=2008-04-28 |work=毎日jp |accessdate=2021-02-04 |language=ja |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080502194109/http://mainichi.jp/enta/mantan/anime/news/20080428mog00m200052000c.html |archivedate=2008-05-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。到了2008年年底統計時，本片以297,927張的特裝版DVD銷量名列年度DVD銷量排行第3名，僅次於歐美片《[[變形金剛_(2007年電影)|變形金剛]]》和《[[神鬼奇航3：世界的盡頭|神鬼奇航3：世界的盡頭]]》雙碟特別版<ref>{{cite web |url=http://contents.oricon.co.jp/music/special/081211_01_06.html |script-title=ja:2008年年間総合DVDランキング |date=2008-12-19 |work=ORICON STYLE |accessdate=2021-02-04 |language=ja |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090303053229/http://contents.oricon.co.jp/music/special/081211_01_06.html |archivedate=2009-03-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。GfK Japan的調查結果稱本片是2008年DVD銷量最高的作品<ref name="GFK">{{Cite web |url=http://www.gfkjpn.co.jp/update_file/pdf/152.pdf |script-title=ja:GfK Certified DVDソフト 2008 発表 |format=pdf |accessdate=2020-12-28 |language=ja |archive-date=2009-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090306173315/http://www.gfkjpn.co.jp/update_file/pdf/152.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。日本地區的[[亚马逊日本|亚马逊日本]]將本片的特裝版DVD列為2008年度最熱賣的DVD<ref>{{cite web|last= Loo|first= Egan|url= https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-12-03/amazon-japan-posts-2008-top-10-dvds-cds-toys|title= Amazon Japan Posts 2008's Top-10 DVDs, CDs, Toys|date= 2008-12-03|work= Anime News Network|access-date= 2009-01-31|language= en|archive-date= 2017-08-02|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170802212820/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-12-03/amazon-japan-posts-2008-top-10-dvds-cds-toys|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

2009年2月20日，《破》上映日期公開的同時<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://eiga.com/news/20090220/3/ |script-title=ja:「ヱヴァンゲリヲン新劇場版：破」6月27日公開！前売券も発売決定 |date=2009-02-20 |publisher=映画.com |accessdate=2021-01-12 |language=ja |archive-date=2014-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140523223652/http://eiga.com/news/20090220/3/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，國王唱片也宣布將於同年5月27日發行《序》的新剪輯版「EVANGELION:1.11」<ref>{{Cite web|script-title=ja:「ヱヴァンゲリヲン 新劇場版：序」が5月27日にBlu-ray/DVD化|url=http://av.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/news/042619.html|accessdate=2021-02-04|author=|date=2009-02-20|last=|format=|work=AV Watch|publisher=|language=ja|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204075131/https://av.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/news/042619.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，包含BD和DVD兩種規格，其中BD是採用[[索尼|索尼]]研發的「Super Bit Mapping for Video（SBMV）」{{refnest|group=註|日文為「{{lang|ja|映像用階調補完技術}}」，根據官網說明，該技術可以透過數位誤差擴散打破色色分明的色帶，對漸層進行有效的平滑處理，提升畫面質感<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.sony.com.tw/zh/electronics/support/articles/S500038744 |title=何謂平滑漸層（Smooth Gradation）？ |publisher=Sony |accessdate=2021-01-12 |language=zh-tw |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930194142/https://www.sony.com.tw/zh/electronics/support/articles/S500038744 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}技術的首例<ref>{{Cite web|script-title=ja:BD版「ヱヴァ新劇場版」に、ソニーのSBMV技術導入|url=http://av.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/news/168327.html|accessdate=2021-02-04|author=|date=2009-05-12|last=|format=|work=AV Watch|publisher=|language=ja|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128162318/https://av.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/news/168327.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。「1.11」版加入了新的鏡頭，因此片長從「1.01」的98分鐘加長至101分鐘。「1.11」版的BD和DVD也都收錄有「1.01」特裝版內附的映像特典「Rebulid of EVANGELION:1.01」，以及新增的《破》劇場版特報等特別收錄。<ref>{{Cite web|script-title=ja:「ヱヴァ新劇場版 1.11」のBD/DVDジャケット公開|url=http://av.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/news/153752.html|accessdate=2021-02-03|author=|date=2009-04-25|last=|format=|work=AV Watch|publisher=|language=ja|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129174335/https://av.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/news/153752.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BDVD"/>

據Oricon的數據顯示，「1.11」版BD在上市首週即賣出4.9萬張，打破歐美片《[[黑暗騎士|黑暗騎士]]》創下的2.9萬張記錄，成為當時日本國內首週銷量最高的BD<ref>{{cite news |url=http://mainichi.jp/enta/mantan/anime/news/20090602mog00m200036000c.html |script-title=ja:ヱヴァンゲリヲン新劇場版：第1部「序」BDが史上最高の初週4.9万枚売り上げ　オリコン |date=2009-06-03 |work=毎日jp |accessdate=2021-02-04 |language=ja |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090606082015/http://mainichi.jp/enta/mantan/anime/news/20090602mog00m200036000c.html |archivedate=2009-06-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。發行三週後銷量來到了6.3萬張，超越《黑暗騎士》以5.6萬張保持的國內BD銷量紀錄<ref>{{cite news |url=http://mainichi.jp/enta/mantan/news/20090616mog00m200047000c.html |script-title=ja:ヱヴァンゲリヲン新劇場版：第1部「序」BDがV3 6万枚突破、史上最高売り上げに |date=2009-06-03 |work=毎日jp |accessdate=2021-02-04 |language=ja |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090618141447/http://mainichi.jp/enta/mantan/news/20090616mog00m200047000c.html |archivedate=2009-06-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。直到2010年2月3日，其國內銷量最高BD的寶座才被紀錄片《[[迈克尔·杰克逊：就是这样|迈克尔·杰克逊：就是这样]]》以26.1萬張的首週成績擠下，而當時「1.11」版BD發行到第34週，國內總銷量也提升至9.9萬張<ref>{{Cite web|script-title=ja:『マイケル・ジャクソンTHISISIT』映像ソフト総売上43億円・104万枚、DVDの初週50万枚突破は『ポニョ』以来|url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/news/73032/full/|accessdate=2021-02-03|author=|date=2010-02-03|format=|work=ORICON NEWS|publisher=|language=ja|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120161041/https://www.oricon.co.jp/news/73032/full/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

台灣地區的家用媒體由[[普威爾國際|普威爾國際]]代理，於2008年7月14日首發VCD、DVD和雙碟盒裝限量版DVD<ref>{{cite web|title=新品發行表|url=http://www.prowaremedia.com.tw/new/sale_list.htm|accessdate=2022-04-03|author=|date=|format=|publisher=[[普威爾國際|普威爾國際]]|language=zh-tw|archive-date=2008-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081102140722/http://www.prowaremedia.com.tw/new/sale_list.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。「1.11」版BD於2010年6月30日發售<ref>{{cite web|title=新片介紹 #福音戰士新劇場版：序1.11|url=http://www.prowaremedia.com.tw/new/product.htm#%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3%E5%BA%8F|accessdate=2020-08-18|author=|date=|format=|publisher=[[普威爾國際|普威爾國際]]|language=zh-tw|archive-date=2019-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191219104207/http://www.prowaremedia.com.tw/new/product.htm#%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3%E5%BA%8F|dead-url=no}}</ref>。香港地區的代理版權由[[亞洲影帶|亞洲影帶]]取得，2008年8月29日VCD（共2片）上市<ref>{{cite web |title=亞洲影帶 |url=http://www.avpnet.com.hk/ |publisher=亞洲影帶 |accessdate=2022-04-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080913161026/http://www.avpnet.com.hk/ |archivedate=2008-09-13 |language=zh-hk |quote=8.29 我們這一家第2輯(V/D)[亞洲]福音戰士新劇場版:序(V)[亞洲]忍風戰隊23-26(完)(V)[亞洲]}}</ref>，DVD分成限量版<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.yesasia.com/us/%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3%E6%88%B0%E5%A3%AB%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%87%E5%A0%B4%E7%89%88-%E5%BA%8F-dvd-%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E5%B9%95-%E9%99%90%E9%87%8F%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E7%89%88-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88/1011081746-0-0-0-zh_TW/info.html |title=福音戰士新劇場版：序 (DVD) (中英文字幕) (限量特別版) (香港版) |publisher=yesasia.com |accessdate=2021-01-22 |language=zh-tw |archive-date=2021-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120161453/https://www.yesasia.com/us/%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3%E6%88%B0%E5%A3%AB%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%87%E5%A0%B4%E7%89%88-%E5%BA%8F-dvd-%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E5%B9%95-%E9%99%90%E9%87%8F%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E7%89%88-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88/1011081746-0-0-0-zh_TW/info.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、普通版<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.yesasia.com/us/%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3%E6%88%B0%E5%A3%AB%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%87%E5%A0%B4%E7%89%88-%E5%BA%8F-dvd-%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E5%B9%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88/1011401655-0-0-0-zh_TW/info.html |title=福音戰士新劇場版：序 (DVD) (中英文字幕) (香港版) |publisher=yesasia.com |accessdate=2021-01-22 |language=zh-tw |archive-date=2008-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081206235059/http://www.yesasia.com/us/%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3%E6%88%B0%E5%A3%AB%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%87%E5%A0%B4%E7%89%88-%E5%BA%8F-dvd-%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E5%B9%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88/1011401655-0-0-0-zh_TW/info.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>和精裝版<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.yesasia.com/us/%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3%E6%88%B0%E5%A3%AB%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%87%E5%A0%B4%E7%89%88-%E5%BA%8F-dvd-%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E5%B9%95-%E7%B2%BE%E8%A3%9D%E7%89%88-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88/1011404237-0-0-0-zh_TW/info.html |title=福音戰士新劇場版：序 (DVD) (中英文字幕) (精裝版) (香港版) |publisher=yesasia.com |accessdate=2021-01-22 |language=zh-tw |archive-date=2021-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120161535/https://www.yesasia.com/us/%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3%E6%88%B0%E5%A3%AB%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%87%E5%A0%B4%E7%89%88-%E5%BA%8F-dvd-%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E5%B9%95-%E7%B2%BE%E8%A3%9D%E7%89%88-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88/1011404237-0-0-0-zh_TW/info.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

北美地區的家用媒體由取得版權的[[Funimation|Funimation]]發行，首先於2009年11月17日推出「1.01」版DVD<ref>{{cite web |title= Evangelion: 1.01 You Are (Not) Alone |url= https://www.amazon.com/Evangelion-1-01-You-Are-Alone/dp/B002KYIAJ2 |publisher= Amazon.com |language= en |accessdate= 2021-01-22 |archive-date= 2016-05-13 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160513051041/http://www.amazon.com/Evangelion-1-01-You-Are-Alone/dp/B002KYIAJ2 |dead-url= no }}</ref>，隨後於2010年3月9日發行「1.11」版的BD<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/encyclopedia/releases.php?id=15638 |title=Evangelion: 1.11 You Are [Not] Alone (Blu-Ray/A) |access-date=2021-01-22 |work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |language=en |archive-date=2019-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517235701/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/encyclopedia/releases.php?id=15638 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在澳大利亞地區，{{link-en|Red Ant Enterprises|Red Ant Enterprises}}於2008年2月宣布取得本片DVD的代理權<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-02-09/australias-red-ant-to-release-evangelion-1.0-on-dvd |title=Australia's Red Ant to Release Evangelion: 1.0 on DVD |date=2008-02-09 |work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |accessdate=2021-01-14 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108070745/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-02-09/australias-red-ant-to-release-evangelion-1.0-on-dvd |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同年11月12日發售<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.red-ant.com.au/ProductFamily.aspx?p=1&ca=246&c1=283&md=4|title=EVANGELION: 1.0 YOU ARE (NOT) ALONE|publisher=REDANT|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081115082447/http://www.red-ant.com.au/ProductFamily.aspx?p=1&ca=246&c1=283&md=4|archive-date=2008-11-15|access-date=2008-09-30|language=en|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。然而該公司在2009年1月進入{{link-en|破產管理|Receivership}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2009-01-23/red-ant-enterprises-enters-into-receivership |title=Red Ant Enterprises enters into receivership |date=2009-01-22 |work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |language=en |accessdate=2021-01-14 |archive-date=2021-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120161021/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2009-01-23/red-ant-enterprises-enters-into-receivership |dead-url=no }}</ref>，代理權移交給{{link-en|Madman Entertainment|Madman Entertainment}}，後者於2009年2月12日發行「1.01」版DVD<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.madman.com.au/actions/catalogue.do?releaseId=12548&method=view |title=Evangelion: 1.01 You Are [Not] Alone. |work=Madman |access-date=2011-10-06 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091203194417/http://www.madman.com.au/actions/catalogue.do?releaseId=12548&method=view |archive-date=2009-12-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

